Package: geneAnnotationMCP
Title: MCP Tools for Human Gene Annotation and GO Queries
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Vince",
           family = "Carey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4046-0063")), person(given="Claude", role="aut"))
Description: Provides Model Context Protocol (MCP) tools for querying human
    gene function and Gene Ontology (GO) annotation. Wraps org.Hs.eg.db and
    GO.db for gene lookup, identifier conversion, GO term retrieval and
    search, and cross-gene functional comparison. Includes an optional
    network-backed search tool via the EBI OLS4 REST API.
